OL,6,FDame Rachel's report, published on
OL,7,FMonday, told of an autistic teenager
OL,8,Fwho was placed by her local authority
OL,9,Fin an Airbnb under supervision for
OL,10,Fnine months following pressure to
OL,11,Fdischarge her from hospital as she did
OL,12,Fnot meet the criteria to be held under
OL,13,Fthe Mental Health Act.
OL,15,FIt also noted an example of a teenage
OL,16,Fgirl who had suffered parental
OL,17,Fdomestic violence and neglect, and
OL,18,Fwho, after experience in foster care
OL,19,Fand a children's home, was given a
OL,20,Fsupervised crisis placement in a
OL,21,Fcaravan.
